column4: b'Today: Mostly sunny, with a high near 60. Calm wind becoming west southwest 5 to 8 mph in the afternoon.'
b'Tonight: A 20 percent chance of showers after 10pm.  Mostly cloudy, with a low around 48. Southwest wind 5 to 7 mph.  New precipitation amounts of less than a tenth of an inch possible.'
b'Friday: A 50 percent chance of showers.  Partly sunny, with a high near 56. West wind around 10 mph.  New precipitation amounts between a tenth and quarter of an inch possible.'
b'Friday Night: A 20 percent chance of showers.  Partly cloudy, with a low around 43. North wind around 6 mph.  New precipitation amounts of less than a tenth of an inch possible.'
b'Saturday: Sunny, with a high near 58. North northeast wind around 7 mph becoming northwest in the afternoon.'
b'Saturday Night: Mostly clear, with a low around 44.'
b'Sunday: Showers likely after 10am.  Mostly cloudy, with a high near 55. Chance of precipitation is 70%.'
b'Sunday Night: Showers likely, mainly before 10pm.  Mostly cloudy, with a low around 44.'
b'Monday: A slight chance of showers.  Partly sunny, with a high near 55.'
